<pol. epia 6.800> pugna oritur : castris litus Romana relictis 
<pol. epia 6.801> agmina in extremum coeunt, clamore vel armis 
<pol. epia 6.802> succursura suis. At quis succursus in armis ? 
<pol. epia 6.803> Unda vetabat iter. Sed enim conspecta suorum 
